== 目标与职能 ==

=== 目标 ===

'''克罗地亚国家银行'''依照[[宪法|宪法]]的规定，在自己的权力和义务的框架内，负责发布国家的[[货币政策|货币政策]]，以维护[[货币|货币]]的稳定和国内外资金的流动性。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hnb.hr/o-hnb/e-opis-hnb.htm#Objectives|title=Objectives of the Croatian National Bank|accessdate=2014-07-05|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|format=|work='''''Croatian National Bank'''''|publisher=|pages=“More about the CNB 章节”|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hnb.hr%2Fo-hnb%2Feo-hnb.htm&date=2014-07-05#Objectives|archivedate=2014-07-05|quote=The objective of the Croatian National Bank is to maintain price stability. Without prejudice to the achievement of its objective, the Croatian National Bank supports the economic policy of the Republic of Croatia, while acting in accordance with the principle of an open market economy with free competition.|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

=== 职能 ===

'''克罗地亚国家银行'''为实现法律赋予之目标而行使的职能为<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hnb.hr/o-hnb/e-opis-hnb.htm#Tasks|title=Tasks of the Croatian National Bank|accessdate=2014-07-05|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|format=|work='''''Croatian National Bank'''''|publisher=|pages=“More about the CNB 章节”|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hnb.hr%2Fo-hnb%2Feo-hnb.htm&date=2014-07-05#Tasks|archivedate=2014-07-05|quote=|deadurl=yes}}</ref>：
*发布以及实施[[货币政策|货币政策]]和外汇政策；
*持有和管理[[外汇储备|外汇储备]]；
*发行[[克罗地亚库纳|克罗地亚库纳]]；
*研究、发布以及维护信贷机构、支付机构、结算机构等金融机构的法规；
*依照法律监督以及管理信贷机构、支付机构、结算机构等金融机构；
*规范和完善支付和结算系统；
*按照法律的规定需要进行的其他活动。

== 组织结构 ==

克罗地亚国家银行的最高决策机构为理事会，理事会共有八名成员，分别为行长、常务副行长及六名副行长；行长为理事会当然主席，负责领导理事会，而理事会其余成员再分别管辖各执行部门<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hnb.hr/o-hnb/e-opis-hnb.htm|title=The Council of the Croatian National Bank|accessdate=2014-07-05|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|trans_title=|format=|work=|publisher='''''Croatian National Bank'''''|pages=“More about the CNB 章节”|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hnb.hr%2Fo-hnb%2Feo-hnb.htm&date=2014-07-05|archivedate=2014-07-05|quote=The Council of the Croatian National Bank consists of eight members, and comprises the Governor, Deputy Governor and six Vicegovernors of the Croatian National Bank. The Council of the Croatian National Bank is competent and responsible for the achievement of the objective and for the carrying out of the tasks of the Croatian National Bank and it defines policies with respect to the activities of the Croatian National Bank.|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。理事会主席及成员全部由[[克罗地亚议会|克罗地亚议会]]任命<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hnb.hr/o-hnb/e-opis-hnb.htm|title=Appointment and status of the members of the CNB Council|accessdate=2014-12-04|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|trans_title=|format=|work=|publisher='''''Croatian National Bank'''''|pages=“More about the CNB 章节”|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hnb.hr%2Fo-hnb%2Feo-hnb.htm&date=2014-07-05|archivedate=2014-07-05|quote=The Governor of the Croatian National Bank is appointed by the Croatian Parliament on the proposal of the Elections, Appointments and Administration Committee, taking into account the opinion of the Finance and Central Budget Committee. The Croatian National Bank has a Deputy Governor and, at most, four Vicegovernors. The Deputy Governor and Vicegovernors are appointed by the Croatian Parliament on the proposal of the Governor of the Croatian National Bank.The external members of the Council of the Croatian National Bank are appointed by the Croatian Parliament on the proposal of the Elections, Appointments and Administration Committee, taking into account the opinion of the Finance and Central Budget Committee.|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。
